reviews.text: Best Korean BBQ in Hong Kong
kind, good taste,clean...wow

I went to Seorae for Kbbq as a party of 3 for dinner on a Thursday night. Although we had for a table, the wait was not long and the service was efficient. We ordered 3 meat mains and they provided vegetables and condiments which was plenty for the three of us.

Service was good, although sometimes can be a bit slow as they are very busy. The food itself was very well seasoned and easy to cook!

The price is slightly expensive (150hkd per person) but well worth it.

All in all Seorae deserves a 5 star.
Food is nice. Staff attitude is good. Only problem is that there is no reception of mobile signal.

Cozy environment, hip crowd, delicious food at excellent value, used to be one of my favorite dinner spots. Unfortunately the service had gone downhill under a control-nazi manager who prioritized her rules over diner experience and neglected on basic things like water refill, air con settings, and basic courtesy.

reviews.text: 因喜愛吃韓燒，而香港較像樣的並不多，而此鋪不時都會前往，但今非昔比，每下愈況。今天點選了喜來烤肉丶五花腩及冷麵。五花腩尚可保持水準，喜來烤肉(牛肉)則祇屬一般，而冷麵則與以往有很大分別，冷麵不冷，以前有些冰碎，當進食時有涼快的感覺，現在已大不如前了。幸好服務仍算不錯，主動幫客人替換鐵板，但最失敗就是衛生方面，洗手間前污水滿地，職買見到亦不作理會，極感失望！
香港有太多韓國燒肉感覺 可以接受 不是特別突出

食物質素不錯，原本打 4 星。
但最後決定打 2 星，全因洗手間污糟到極點，一蹋糊塗，不知所謂，道致完全喪失享受美食嘅心情，食慾全消。
喜來稀肉 位於百利達廣場地庫 提供高質韓燒 有Ｄ貴 ！
食物好味，服務好，有禮貌！😋😋
